%h1 Privacy Policy

.row
  .col-md-12
    %p
      At our company, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our services. Please read this policy carefully to understand our practices regarding your personal data.

    %h2 Information We Collect
    %p We may collect the following types of information:
    %ul
      %li
        %strong Personal Information:
        When you register an account, make a purchase, or contact us, we may collect personal information such as your name, email address, postal address, phone number, and payment details.
      %li
        %strong Usage Information:
        We may collect information about how you use our website, including your IP address, browser type, referring/exit pages, operating system, and date/time stamps.
      %li
        %strong Cookies and Similar Technologies:
        We use cookies and similar tracking technologies to enhance your browsing experience and collect information about your preferences and interactions with our website. Please refer to our
        = link_to "Cookie Policy", cookies_path
        for more details.

    %h2 How We Use Your Information
    %p We may use the information we collect for the following purposes:
    %ul
      %li To provide and maintain our services, process transactions, and fulfill your requests.
      %li To communicate with you, respond to your inquiries, and provide customer support.
      %li To personalize your experience and deliver relevant content and advertisements.
      %li To analyze and improve our website, services, and business operations.
      %li To detect, prevent, and address technical issues and protect against fraudulent or illegal activities.

    %h2 Information Sharing and Disclosure
    %p We may share your information in the following circumstances:
    %ul
      %li With third-party service providers who assist us in operating our website and providing our services.
      %li With law enforcement agencies, government authorities, or other third parties when required by law or to protect our rights, property, or safety.
      %li In connection with a merger, acquisition, or sale of all or a portion of our assets.
    %p We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties for their marketing purposes without your explicit consent.

    %h2 Data Security
    %p
      We implement reasonable security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

    %h2 Your Choices and Rights
    %p You have the following choices and rights regarding your personal information:
    %ul
      %li You can update or correct your account information by logging into your account settings.
      %li You can opt out of receiving promotional emails from us by following the unsubscribe instructions provided in the emails.
      %li You have the right to request access to, rectification, or erasure of your personal information, subject to certain limitations.
      %li You have the right to object to or restrict the processing of your personal information in certain circumstances.

    %h2 Children's Privacy
    %p
      Our website and services are not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child without parental consent, we will take steps to remove that information from our servers.

    %h2 Changes to this Privacy Policy
    %p
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting a notice on our website or sending you an email. We encourage you to review this policy periodically for any updates.

